<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/w/index.php?title=Special:Upload&amp;wpDestFile=Robert.ludlum.jpg" class="new" title="File:Robert.ludlum.jpg">File:Robert.ludlum.jpg</a><br /></td>
