<li><i>The Paris Option</i> (with <a href="/wiki/Gayle_Lynds" title="Gayle Lynds">Gayle Lynds</a>) (2002)</li>
<li><i>The Altman Code</i> (with <a href="/wiki/Gayle_Lynds" title="Gayle Lynds">Gayle Lynds</a>) (2003)</li>
